    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来到1970年代的法国南部，化身新手私家侦探，发掘一位顽固老先生的种种秘密。一路抽丝剥茧、见机而行——询问目击证人，分辨谁在说谎，针对其动机作出假设，最后与逃避过往之人当面对质，让他们不再保持沉默。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >诡异委托，离奇展开</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >历史教授维克多·杜瓦隆（Victor Dousvalon）对你提出超乎寻常的委托：深入调查“他本人”的过往。这位老先生向来擅长隐藏自己的神秘经历，就连他的女儿凯瑟琳都所知甚少。一场看似无害的意外让他有所顿悟，决定雇用你来协助凯瑟琳，共同追溯他人生中的点点滴滴。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>既然是他的亲身经历，为何不直接说给女儿听？</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>凯瑟琳已跟父亲疏离多年，怎么会突然想了解他的生平？ </i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>你的第一起案件想必会相当棘手……</i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不择手段，打破沉默！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >全神贯注展开侦探调查，翻找家族文件，刺探个人隐私，不时叨扰调查对象，总之就是要打听出所有蛛丝马迹。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/7ac10efea93e6884a93b1b9055705f8e.poster.avif?t=1752685808\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/7ac10efea93e6884a93b1b9055705f8e.webm?t=1752685808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/7ac10efea93e6884a93b1b9055705f8e.mp4?t=1752685808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >勇往直前，抽丝剥茧</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你无法袖手旁观，眼看其他角色帮你想出答案，好好证明自己的推理能力吧。选择特定线索，看是要追查到底，还是点到为止。你必须非常善于诱导，才能促使这些人打破沉默！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/4f7aba2e338990518e808b954188a118.poster.avif?t=1752685808\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/4f7aba2e338990518e808b954188a118.webm?t=1752685808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/4f7aba2e338990518e808b954188a118.mp4?t=1752685808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >认识角色，追寻历史</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拼凑他们的人生拼图，体会他们做过的选择，找出他们不愿面对的憾事，设身处地走访调查。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你不是从上帝视角鸟瞰众人，而是近距离持续观察他们独特的生存处世之道，探索这些角色耐人寻味的过往。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/af7fe448e3a291a0e91fb91bf5aa9cd9.poster.avif?t=1752685808\" width=610 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/af7fe448e3a291a0e91fb91bf5aa9cd9.webm?t=1752685808\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114300/extras/af7fe448e3a291a0e91fb91bf5aa9cd9.mp4?t=1752685808\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
